uk.co.saiman.utilities

Interface Configurable<C>

  • Type Parameters:
    C - The configuration interface type
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ExperimentPart<C,I,O>, StatefulConfigurable<C,S>

    public interface Configurable<C>
    Implementation of this API designates a class which is configurable by a given configuration interface type.
